article.headline: Texas-Pan American 67, N.C. Central 66
article.story: EDINBURG, Texas -- Julius Allgood hit a jump shot at the buzzer to give Texas-Pan American a 67-66 win over North Carolina Central on Saturday night. Allgood scored 14 for Texas Pan-American (8-16). Emmanuel Jones and Jared Maree each scored 13 while Nathan Hawkins added 11 and Nick Weiermiller got 10. Jones also had 10 rebounds. Bryan Ayala scored 22 for North Carolina Central (2-25). Jamar Briscoe got 19. Texas Pan-American shot 50 percent from the field while North Carolina Central shot 45 percent.
